## 7.  Dance Twist

Play a sound clip and do a body twist.

- ![](07/dancer-01.png)
- ![](07/dancer-02.png)

- Get ready
  - Choose an image of a person ready to dance.
  - Choose or record a sound clip.Keep it short!
- Try this code
  - ![](07/code.png)
  - Chose whirl from the menu.
- Do it
  - Press the key to start.

