- Try this code
  - ![](09/code.png)
- Do it
  - Click the sprite to duplicate the costume.

## 10.  Moving animation

Animate a character as it moves.


- Get ready
  - Click to open the sprite library.
  - Choose a sprite that has 2 or more costumes.
- Try this code
  - ![](10/code.png)
- Extra tip
  - Does your sprite look upside-down?
  - You can change its rotation style.
  - Click the .
  - all around
  - left-right
  - don't rotate

## 11.  Surprise Button

Make your own button.

- Get ready
  - Choose a drum (from the Things category).
  - You can change the name of your sprite.
- Try this code
  - ![](11/code.png)
  - Insert the "Pick random" block.
- Do it
  - Click to see (and hear) what it does.

